    <div>
        
        
            <h2 style="	margin-top: 2.0em;
">About ACS Advocacy</h2>
<p>The ACS Government Affairs communicates and highlights the vital role of chemistry and its practitioners to policy and lawmakers to gain deeper knowledge and responsible use of science and encourage and support the active participation of ACS members in public outreach efforts.</p>

        
    </div>
    
